      "content": "DONE — Task 88: Add type field to bus messages\n\nFiles changed:\n- src/db.ts: added `type TEXT` migration, `Message.type` field, `MessageType` type alias, `detectMessageType()` helper, updated `insertMessage` prepared statement and `sendMessage()` signature (new optional `type` param), updated `postMilestoneOnce()` to pass detected type\n- src/mcp-server.ts: added `type` param to send_message tool schema and handler; passes through to sendMessage\n- public/app.js: renders a colored badge in message header for non-plain types (done/blocked/decision/finding/commit)\n- public/style.css: added `.msg-type-badge` + per-type color classes\n\nBuild: tsc passes clean.\nCommit: 05d5741 in .synapse/worktrees/developer-msg-types (branch synapse/developer-msg-types)",
